{"tid":2506484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊文重推] 80年前有班人喺香港打咗場好慘烈嘅戰爭","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T15:43:41.000Z","uid":43150,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7437ed30b22046e6ab661eed049626bf765b1b","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:46:47.000Z","msg":"80年前，即係1941年，日軍進攻香港，英加印港及各國軍人奮起保衛家園，史稱<strong>香港保衛戰</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/images/%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89-75-%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E4%BF%9D%E8%A1%9B%E6%88%B0%E9%81%BA%E8%B7%A1%E8%88%87%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fimages%2F%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2585%2589-75-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%2581%25BA%25E8%25B7%25A1%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=0dd9389b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fimages%2F%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2585%2589-75-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%2581%25BA%25E8%25B7%25A1%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%2F&h=01000801\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/images/%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89-75-%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E4%BF%9D%E8%A1%9B%E6%88%B0%E9%81%BA%E8%B7%A1%E8%88%87%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2/</a><br />\n<strong>【圖片故事】香港重光 75 周年 保衛戰遺跡與歷史</strong><br />\n今日（8 月 30 日）是香港重光紀念日 75 周年，在武漢肺炎疫情的影響下，今年未有大型的紀念儀式，仍有市民自發到中環和平紀念碑為二戰犧牲的軍人獻花。香港從二戰重光自今多年，這段歷史或多或少已被部分人遺忘。然而，緊扣香港歷史的二戰防衛遺跡卻一直存在郊遊的山徑之中，網上專頁「Watershed Hong Kong」，嘗試藉這些遺址去訴說這段被忽視的歷史。他們平時會穿着軍服帶導賞團，到戰時遺跡訴說當時的歷史故事，以民間角度承傳香港保衛戰歷史。專頁成員 Kevin 說：「一定要認識你嘅過去，先可以創造新嘅未來。」<br />\n<br />\n1941 年日本發動太平洋戰爭，先偷襲美國珍珠港，繼而在 1941 年 12 月 8 日由廣東入侵當時為英國殖民地的香港。香港約 13,000 名來自英國、印度、加拿大及華人組成的守軍，面對 50,000 多精銳的日軍作出頑強抵抗，最後還是無法扭轉局勢。總督楊慕琦爵士於 12 月 25 日決定投降，這場維持 18 日的激烈戰事，稱為香港保衛戰。<br />\n<br />\n在保衛戰中，香港義勇防衛軍（Hong Kong Volunteer Defence Corps）有着重要的角色，軍團在 1854 年成立，初時為「香港義勇軍」，當時是為因應駐港英軍被調派參與克里米亞戰爭而成立，以填補香港的防務空缺，成員大部分是居住在香港的英國人。至 1878 年成為常設的香港本地後備軍，1917年規定在香港居住的英國適齡男性必須加入，到1920年代改組為「香港義勇防衛軍」，成員本身自己有正常工作，但願意貢獻工餘時間保衛家園，甚至犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n「Watershed Hong Kong」創辦人 Taurus 說：「認識香港保衛戰，令香港人對公民義務及公民意識認識多一點。」香港教育中的歷史觀甚少詳細提及本土歷史，而香港主權移交後，特區政府亦取消了香港重光紀念日。日後郊遊時經過這些遺跡，不妨停留觀察一下。它們不但盛載着香港保衛戰的歷史，亦提醒着我們戰爭衝突中為保護家園犧牲的軍人及平民。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/2M_oF6xN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F2M_oF6xN_1200x0.png&h=7f8f5aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃泥涌峽徑的其中一間營房，部份營房內有上下格床，似曾經被人居住。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/3M_K36ax_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F3M_K36ax_1200x0.png&h=5fd8f510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少營房內，仍留有戰時軍人休息用的吊床掛鉤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/4M_d5XNq_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F4M_d5XNq_1200x0.png&h=8c0033bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「Watershed Hong Kong」 成員 Franco 為了更生動介紹香港保衛戰，特意穿上戰時英軍軍服作導賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/27_gEtsP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F27_gEtsP_1200x0.png&h=0fe3b177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港戰役期間，日軍炮轟香港島。（相片由香港浸會大學歷史系副教授鄺智文提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/85080730_10157884938148550_8210418847795118080_o_9f39x_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F85080730_10157884938148550_8210418847795118080_o_9f39x_1200x0.png&h=127fa2c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1941年，華砲兵五十週年紀念會操（相片由香港浸會大學歷史系副教授鄺智文提供）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/7M_gESYc_1200x0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F7M_gESYc_1200x0.png&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=75131b2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F7M_gESYc_1200x0.png&h=c0c74b0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/7M_gESYc_1200x0.png</a><br />\n黃泥涌峽徑附近，其中一個機槍堡的內部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/8M_7mPKg_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F8M_7mPKg_1200x0.png&h=ed508c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日軍攻擊守軍通常會將手榴彈投入機槍堡頂部的通風管，裏面的軍人就會全軍覆沒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/34_SHPBq_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F34_SHPBq_1200x0.png&h=7f35fc72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1941年的香港防衛軍傳訊隊（相片由香港浸會大學歷史系副教授鄺智文提供）"},{"pid":"289120ec922b3c8227e8900d00a8a0192f56a10d","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/10M_L6c3k_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F10M_L6c3k_1200x0.png&h=faebddd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在城門碉堡其中一條地道可見「若林隊占領」的刻字，若林東一是當年攻佔城門碉堡的日軍隊長。攻城門碉堡不是若林隊的任務，當他的軍隊到達此處發現只有約 30 名英軍駐守，便私自突襲，不到一天便完成佔領。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/11M_cFirC_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F11M_cFirC_1200x0.png&h=b4c687a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英軍曾反鎖在城門碉堡的炮兵觀察所內，後來日軍用炸藥炸開石門，有兩名印度炮兵身亡，其後日軍再投擲手榴彈攻擊，現在觀察所的牆上仍留下不少手榴彈爆開的痕跡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/12M_ejRF5_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F12M_ejRF5_1200x0.png&h=dc2a586f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摩星嶺防空炮台軍營於 1941 年 12 月 11 日至 16 日，曾多次被日軍空襲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Mount_Davis_Battery_F2_uksiE_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FMount_Davis_Battery_F2_uksiE_1200x0.png&h=f25b7a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摩星嶺炮台的一門 9.2 吋口徑海防炮，最大射程是19.2公里（網絡圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/14M_ME3Ur_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F14M_ME3Ur_1200x0.png&h=40911760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摩星嶺其中一個營房內的洗手間和廚房，原本有牆分隔兩個地方，後來被人佔用而被打通。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/15M_BMGCl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F15M_BMGCl_1200x0.png&h=086c729e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃泥涌內，其中一個軍藥庫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/16M_jDLJB_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F16M_jDLJB_1200x0.png&h=eb75908d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於新界的城門戰地遺跡其中兩個隧道出入口：麗晶街（左）和舒佛畢利巷（右）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/17M_gsvPv_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F17M_gsvPv_1200x0.png&h=062cbee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020 年 8 月 30 日是香港重光紀念日 75 周年，網上專頁「Watershed Hong Kong」成員和區議員伍健偉，李俊威和方浩軒自發到中環和平紀念碑為二戰犧牲的軍人獻花。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/18M_U4CHm_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F18M_U4CHm_1200x0.png&h=02994820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「Watershed Hong Kong」 創辦人之一 Taurus 和成員 Kevin，在中環和平紀念碑前鞠躬獻花。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/19M_cRzaT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F19M_cRzaT_1200x0.png&h=7cc9f27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有組織在柴灣歌連臣角西灣國殤紀念墳場悼念二戰中為香港犧牲的軍人，軍人中有不同國籍例如來自加拿大和印度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20M_LY1Wx_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20M_LY1Wx_1200x0.png&h=bbfed0a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柴灣歌連臣角西灣國殤紀念墳場。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/21M_IhcWQ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F21M_IhcWQ_1200x0.png&h=6e772ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020 年的疫情下，戴防毒面具的市民細閱參與保衛戰各國犧牲軍人的名單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/22M_pjvYj_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F22M_pjvYj_1200x0.png&h=6870bcdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西灣國殤紀念墳場內，有為香港義勇防衛軍立的墓碑。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screenshot202020-08-3020at204.56.0320PM_pogfo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreenshot202020-08-3020at204.56.0320PM_pogfo_1200x0.png&h=7673cce1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n1945 年 8 月 30 日，皇家海軍迅敏號輕巡洋艦並隨同海軍少將夏愨抵達香港，標誌著日治時期的結束，香港重光 &copy; IWM A 30539<br />\n<br />\n攝影：oiyan chan<br />\n資料來源：香港浸會大學歷史系鄺智文副教授、<br />\nWatershed Hong Kong、Imperial War Museums"},{"pid":"ffbde0ceb192e508c525e25b4db267c5b7fd9590","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人"},{"pid":"cf0208526b867e3ea6546f901d01a5d3b79de6f6","tid":2506484,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4217b3ab56ac7cac33b5ea591ca3f7477a56e7da","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636b57715af0d0f3d96b0968224981fa95949369","tid":2506484,"uid":191661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe840dffa11cfc2aa345c5b9cb82ae369cb5e7d4","tid":2506484,"uid":46120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c5c2024fd0b3f79120e68faf58133febb13a4dfe","tid":2506484,"uid":210121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ff14ef184b72dc6f473a7bfb1afd215f7f07c025","tid":2506484,"uid":370107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745c8275b53b68312e806d1d7f0c72db003ec73a","tid":2506484,"uid":161711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"34612969e2f2986ad73a50fe0a57a1fca0ee976f","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/10M_L6c3k_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F10M_L6c3k_1200x0.png&h=faebddd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在城門碉堡其中一條地道可見「若林隊占領」的刻字，若林東一是當年攻佔城門碉堡的日軍隊長。攻城門碉堡不是若林隊的任務，當他的軍隊到達此處發現只有約 30 名英軍駐守，便私自突襲，不到一天便完成佔領。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n日本帝國陸軍傳奇若林東一<br />\n<a href=\"http://rthk9.rthk.hk/elearning/ecotour/tour06/route06_point05.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frthk9.rthk.hk%2Felearning%2Fecotour%2Ftour06%2Froute06_point05.htm&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=70e9c14f\" target=\"_blank\">http://rthk9.rthk.hk/elearning/ecotour/tour06/route06_point05.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n欣賞過白千層林的景色後，繼續走那曲折多灣的林道，直到經過主壩及燒烤場後，會見到麥理浩徑第六段的指示牌，從這裡往金山方向上山走的話，大家可會發現一些特別的人工建築？原來這些頹垣敗瓦，就是香港在二次世界大戰時所剩下的戰時遺跡之一。<br />\n<br />\n城門碉堡屬於醉酒線防線一部分，位於城門水塘南方。由於碉堡所在處為防線是整條防線比較薄弱部分，因此英軍在山坡以鋼筋及水泥興建了碉堡。雖然城門碉堡在大戰前預計可以堅守兩星期，但最終日軍卻在數小時之內已攻下碉堡，碉堡以至整條醉酒灣防線的失陷，加上日軍的空襲，導致守軍南撤至香港島。<br />\n<br />\n如今城門碉堡尚存，只是部分地道已被沙泥堵塞，若走進地道內，你會發現全以倫敦地名、街名及酒店名命名，而其中一條地道入口更可見到「若林隊占領」的刻字，這就是當年率先攻佔城門碉堡的日軍二二八聯隊第十中隊的隊長若林東一*。<br />\n<br />\n英軍也好，日軍也好，他們遺下的刻字都極具歷史價值，大家實在要保護這些戰地遺跡。<br />\n<br />\n離開碉堡後，沿路下山返回城門道上，也是結束旅程的時間了，只要沿城門道走，便可返回菠蘿壩小巴總站乘車離去。<br />\n<br />\n*原本佔領城門碉堡的任務並不是由若林隊負責，但他率軍到達時發現此處防守鬆懈，只有約三十名英軍，所以違抗軍令私自突襲碉堡，只用了約十小時便完全佔據。"},{"pid":"ce9de25d872d06ebb51fea3766fcbf095e0829e0","tid":2506484,"uid":378294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"陣間班祟日野孫就走出黎話日治先係最好既時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85419c180c22f394acba6f7cd3ed5e1c5941f2ca","tid":2506484,"uid":278085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:41:10.000Z","msg":"啱啱响YouTube 發現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ljWkVe_Milc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FljWkVe_Milc&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=51f7f2aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ljWkVe_Milc</a>"},{"pid":"94fc52432b17d06c021583c5067e89297fb040f3","tid":2506484,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:43:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b1f3efd3c8ddae66eeaa70f0b154e07566b7c58","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記一眾衛港英烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wetoasthk.com/%e3%80%90%e8%bb%8d%e4%ba%8b%e5%bb%ba%e7%af%89%e3%80%91%e8%a5%bf%e7%81%a3%e5%9c%8b%e6%ae%a4%e7%b4%80%e5%bf%b5%e5%a2%b3%e5%a0%b4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%25bb%258d%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e7%25af%2589%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e7%2581%25a3%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%25ae%25a4%25e7%25b4%2580%25e5%25bf%25b5%25e5%25a2%25b3%25e5%25a0%25b4%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=a8cb50ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wetoasthk.com/%e3%80%90%e8%bb%8d%e4%ba%8b%e5%bb%ba%e7%af%89%e3%80%91%e8%a5%bf%e7%81%a3%e5%9c%8b%e6%ae%a4%e7%b4%80%e5%bf%b5%e5%a2%b3%e5%a0%b4/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%8B%E6%AE%A4%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E5%A2%B3%E5%A0%B4_website.png?w=773&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AE%25A4%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E5%25A2%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B4_website.png%3Fw%3D773%26ssl%3D1&h=52ee9df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【軍事建築】西灣國殤紀念墳場<br />\n回顧歷史，香港有幸不乏為捍衛腳下土地而犧牲的烈士。<strong>有人以死明志，亦有人堅守崗位直至最後一刻。</strong>香港保衛戰，一直在不同時代上演。<br />\n<br />\n1941 年 12 月，日軍偷襲珍珠港，發動太平洋戰爭，並進犯本港。當時駐防香港之部隊主要由英軍、加拿大軍，以及英屬印度軍所組成。除此以外，本地華人及混血兒亦加入保衛香港的行列。華洋軍人無分彼此，於前線及後勤崗位奮戰，竭力守衛我城。<strong>經過 18 日激戰，由於守軍寡不敵眾，市區斷水斷糧，時任港督楊慕琦（Sir Mark Aitchison Young）無奈於聖誕日投降。在戰鬥期間，大量華洋軍人犧牲，尤其於黃泥涌峽，香港防衛軍遭受慘重傷亡，加軍准將羅遜（Brigadier John Kelburne Lawson）更於由指揮部突圍期間被日軍包圍，力戰陣亡。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F1-1.jpg&h=17dc8a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅遜准將之墓<br />\n<br />\n更甚的是，在三年零八個月的日治期間，有大量軍民於戰俘營及集中營裡遭受各種折磨，包括營養不良、疾病、虐待，及遭處決。戰後，位處柴灣以南的西灣國殤紀念墳場落成，戰時蒙難的軍人和平民才得以妥善安葬。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>西灣國殤紀念墳場共有 1578 座墳墓，長眠於該處的英魂包括陸、海、空軍，商船隊隊員，以及本地軍民。他們之中有英國人、加拿大人、印度人、澳洲人、紐西蘭人、緬甸人、荷蘭人，以及香港人。</strong>墳場入口亦建有西灣紀念碑，碑上刻有 2071 位未知葬身何處的軍人的姓名，當中包括英軍 1319 名、加軍 228 名、印軍 287 名，以及 237 名香港軍人。另外，入口位置有兩塊碑石，分別紀念已火葬的印度教和錫克教軍人，以及於兩次大戰中在中國殉難後無法保存遺骸的英聯邦軍人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F4.jpg&h=59bece98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墳場正面<br />\n<br />\n由於在開戰前夕，加拿大曾派遣兩營軍隊赴港協防，且大量加軍在港戰死，因此在05、09、12及16年，當時的加拿大總理訪港時曾前往西灣國殤紀念墳場悼念陣亡將士。外國政府首腦尚且親身向烈士致意，何況是吾等香港市民？<strong>和平得來不易，現今香港人所享有的自由乃源於前人艱苦的奮鬥，因此我們不能將衛港英烈的犧牲置之於腦後，忘記得一乾二淨。相反，我們要瞭解烈士背後的故事及犧牲的因由，懷有感激之意和尊重之心，並繼承英烈衛港之志。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F2.jpg&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=9fa87057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i2.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2.jpg</a></strong><br />\n無名軍人之墓<br />\n<br />\n西灣國殤紀念墳場鄰近市區，可從柴灣地鐵站步行而至，且設有傳意牌簡介保衛戰的歷史，歡迎大家親身到墳場了解更多有關香港保衛戰的故事，並向衛港英魂致意。唯有銘記烈士的犧牲，才使他們的付出不致白費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F3.jpg&h=537bc781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豎立於墓碑前的傳意牌<br />\n<br />\n位置：鄰近柴灣華人永遠墳場<br />\n<br />\n交通：柴灣地鐵站 A 出口，經行人天橋至青年廣場，到達地面後橫過環翠道，沿連城道步行至華人永遠墳場，轉右沿歌連臣角道直上。<br />\n<br />\n開放時間：上午 8 時至下午 5 時<br />\n<br />\n<strong>除西灣國殤紀念墳場外，本港亦建有歌連臣角軍人墳場，赤柱軍人墳場及廓爾喀軍人墳場（廓爾喀即啹喀）。</strong>以上墳場均由英聯邦戰爭公墓委員會管理，惟只有西灣國殤紀念墳場及赤柱軍人墳場於平日恆常開放予公眾參觀。除上述墳場外，亦有軍人長眠於本港其他墳場，例如在<strong>鑽石山墳場之抗日烈士墓內，其中五名殉難者為姓名可考之英軍服務團華籍成員（分別為陳鴻照、戴家賢、仇伙、劉江、吳德璋，其中戴家賢應為別名）。他們悉數於 1944 年秋（10 月 31 日）遭日人處決，無緣目睹一年後香港重光。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F5.jpg&h=230f2e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑽石山墳場之抗日烈士墓。(圖片來源：Gwulo)"},{"pid":"a8ef0b39916d9f5528b74c5c063757e2b0d176ef","tid":2506484,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca74417d65ce70241940a9aebc07bff9578bc0f","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"海防博物館舉行英軍服務團情報草圖展（附圖）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  情報工作常給人一種神秘感，但在戰爭期間，軍事情報對軍事部署、防禦建置，以至軍事力量等更起着關鍵性的影響力。市民如對二次大戰時期，英軍服務團的情報工作感到興趣的話，就不要錯過現在起至明年三月十六日於香港海防博物館舉行的「英軍服務團情報草圖展」。<br />\n<br />\n  展覽展出澳洲戰爭紀念館借出的三十八幅英軍服務團刺探日軍軍事情報的草圖，以介紹二次大戰時的戰況，以及英軍服務團的工作。展出的草圖因逃避日軍和漢奸的耳目，體積非常細小，但畫工仔細，資料豐富，對抗日勝利影響深遠，難得一見。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>  英軍服務團的創立人為英軍上校賴廉士。</strong>他於一九四一年香港淪陷後被拘禁在深水埗戰俘集中營，但旋即逃脫。他翻山越嶺，繞過沙田，抵達西貢後乘船離開香港水域，到達大鵬灣北岸的鯊魚涌。在中共游擊隊的協助下，從國民黨政府管轄區惠州輾轉到達戰時廣東省的臨時省會曲江（即今韶關），並在該地成立了英軍服務團。<br />\n<br />\n  當時，參與英軍服務團的軍官均擁有在香港及中國作戰的經驗。<strong>他們除了協助香港的英國戰俘、集中營被拘禁的人士逃亡外，更組織情報人員，潛回香港淪陷區刺探日軍的情報，對盟軍在第二次世界大戰裡取得最終勝利貢獻良多。</strong>一九四五年八月，日本宣布無條件投降，英軍服務團成員參與接收香港的工作，於同年十二月三十一日解散。<br />\n<br />\n  戰後，賴廉士上校把在二戰期間搜集得來的抗日軍事情報草圖原件悉數捐贈予坎培拉澳洲戰爭紀念館。是次展覽展出部分珍貴的情報草圖。這些情報圖顯示出各受監視的建築物描繪細緻，其周遭環境、地勢及地理位置、所駐守的人員數目、存放物資的種類及存量等均有詳細記錄，足見所得資料並非由一名情報員獨力在一個短促的時段內能搜集得來。而製成的情報圖，每每會交到對圖中記錄的地點或建築毫無認識的人員以作跟進，對方可能會憑此來進行空襲轟炸，或防避日軍的軍事還擊，或用之來相約組織內的其他成員在特定的地點交換情報。此外，為求能易於傳遞而不被日軍搜獲，此等情報圖須繪畫在細小的紙張上，因此有必要作出仔細的描繪和詳盡而扼要的描述。由此可見盟軍能取得最終的勝利，實是眾志成城的結果。<br />\n<br />\n  海防博物館位於香港筲箕灣東喜道175號，開放時間為每日上午十時至下午五時，逢星期四休館〈公眾假期除外〉。入場費十元，全日制學生、殘疾人士及六十歲或以上高齡人士可獲半價優惠。逢星期三免費入場。<br />\n<br />\n  有關展覽詳情，可瀏覽該館網址 hk.coastaldefence.museum 或致電二五六九 一五○○查詢。<br />\n完<br />\n２０１０年９月２２日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間１９時１５分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201009/22/P201009220199.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201009%2F22%2FP201009220199.htm&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=cc2773b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201009/22/P201009220199.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201009/22/P201009220199_photo_1020604.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201009%2F22%2FP201009220199_photo_1020604.JPG&h=cd5097a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201009/22/P201009220199_photo_1020606.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201009%2F22%2FP201009220199_photo_1020606.JPG&h=8f7590da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201009/22/P201009220199_photo_1020605.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201009%2F22%2FP201009220199_photo_1020605.JPG&h=01fa9739&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de2c2cb2d2e2fa6d3e6cb39876d82e1b7018798a","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85419c180c22f394acba6f7cd3ed5e1c5941f2ca","tid":2506484,"uid":278085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:41:10.000Z","msg":"啱啱响YouTube 發現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ljWkVe_Milc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FljWkVe_Milc&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=51f7f2aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ljWkVe_Milc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"This channel is good"},{"pid":"c477127256f69254142ca2109da5e1fa12230538","tid":2506484,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c719f2c0ec1d04bc61a65d638ab09c83d079b9e","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:19:20.000Z","msg":"戰時香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThanks to Imperial War Museum, UK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.iwm.org.uk/ciim5/148/155/mid_000000.jpg?action=e&amp;cat=Art&quot; alt=&quot;Hong Kong\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.iwm.org.uk%2Fciim5%2F148%2F155%2Fmid_000000.jpg%3Faction%3De%26cat%3DArt%22%20alt%3D%22Hong%20Kong&h=98513a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.iwm.org.uk/ciim5/186/675/mid_000000.jpg?action=e&amp;cat=Art&quot; alt=&quot;Hong Kong\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.iwm.org.uk%2Fciim5%2F186%2F675%2Fmid_000000.jpg%3Faction%3De%26cat%3DArt%22%20alt%3D%22Hong%20Kong&h=67b32a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/19693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwm.org.uk%2Fcollections%2Fitem%2Fobject%2F19693&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=4f28b3f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/19693</a>"},{"pid":"2a9a17499660396da972ec75d07a7b02e45c56ba","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"Imperial War Museum <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.iwm.org.uk/ciim5/751/105/mid_HU_002779.jpg?action=e&amp;cat=Photographs&quot; alt=&quot;THE BATTLE OF HONG KONG, DECEMBER 1941\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.iwm.org.uk%2Fciim5%2F751%2F105%2Fmid_HU_002779.jpg%3Faction%3De%26cat%3DPhotographs%22%20alt%3D%22THE%20BATTLE%20OF%20HONG%20KONG%2C%20DECEMBER%201941&h=d943de95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBritish prisoners of war marching to captivity in Hong Kong, 29 December 1941.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/205087121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwm.org.uk%2Fcollections%2Fitem%2Fobject%2F205087121&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=de1a3904\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/205087121</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.iwm.org.uk/ciim5/253/116/mid_000000.jpg?action=e&amp;cat=Souvenirs%20and%20ephemera&quot; alt=&quot;shorts, handmade, Far East Civilian Internee\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.iwm.org.uk%2Fciim5%2F253%2F116%2Fmid_000000.jpg%3Faction%3De%26cat%3DSouvenirs%2520and%2520ephemera%22%20alt%3D%22shorts%2C%20handmade%2C%20Far%20East%20Civilian%20Internee&h=5016a7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHandmade shorts improvised from the remnants of flour sacks, associated with the service of Archibald Elston who had been Assistant Superintendant in the Hong Kong Police before being made a civilian internee in Stanley Camp, Hong Kong during the Second World War.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/30080861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwm.org.uk%2Fcollections%2Fitem%2Fobject%2F30080861&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=a7c69452\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/30080861</a><br />\n<br />\nAmerican, British and Dutch bankers being marched to their offices by the Japanese during the liquidation of enemy banks in Hong Kong. Long before the Japanese assault on Hong Kong on 8 December 1941 the colony had been considered by the British as an outpost which would be virtually indefensible in time of war. General Maltby, Commanding Officer of the Hong Kong garrison, surrendered to the Japanese on 25 December 1941.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/205086921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwm.org.uk%2Fcollections%2Fitem%2Fobject%2F205086921&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=509446d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/205086921</a>"},{"pid":"e6c618a5db322f0c8221226eb291d69a173d4b54","tid":2506484,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"唔知當時香港人見到咁有咩諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.iwm.org.uk/ciim5/38/91/mid_000000.jpg?action=e&amp;cat=Photographs&quot; alt=&quot;THE BATTLE OF HONG KONG, DECEMBER 1941\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.iwm.org.uk%2Fciim5%2F38%2F91%2Fmid_000000.jpg%3Faction%3De%26cat%3DPhotographs%22%20alt%3D%22THE%20BATTLE%20OF%20HONG%20KONG%2C%20DECEMBER%201941&h=77d7f4f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJapanese troops enter Hong Kong led by Lieutenant General Takashi Sakai and Vice Admiral Miimi Massichi, 26 December 1941.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/205195081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwm.org.uk%2Fcollections%2Fitem%2Fobject%2F205195081&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=917dc4d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/205195081</a><br />\n加拿大手足<im